Company Overview of Third Point LLC



Snapshot People




Company Overview
Third Point LLC is an employee owned hedge fund sponsor. The firm primarily provides its services to pooled investment vehicles. It also caters to insurance companies, separately managed accounts, and non 40 act investment company. The firm typically invests in the public equity and fixed income markets across the globe. The firm primarily invests by employing event driven value oriented strategy. It also makes real estate investments. The firm conducts fundamental research to make its investments Third Point LLC was founded in 1995 and is based in New York City with additional offices in New York City, Sunnyvale, California; Los Angeles, California; Stamford, Connecticut; Bangalore, India, ...
Third Point LLC is an employee owned hedge fund sponsor. The firm primarily provides its services to pooled investment vehicles. It also caters to insurance companies, separately managed accounts, and non 40 act investment company. The firm typically invests in the public equity and fixed income markets across the globe. The firm primarily invests by employing event driven value oriented strategy. It also makes real estate investments. The firm conducts fundamental research to make its investments Third Point LLC was founded in 1995 and is based in New York City with additional offices in New York City, Sunnyvale, California; Los Angeles, California; Stamford, Connecticut; Bangalore, India, and Hong Kong.
